ygData.messageBody:
Druids are a POWER lvlers dream come true.. they can solo reds easy with the use of spirit of wolf and those wonderful DOT's :) I can get a druid to lvl 20 in 4 to 5 days of /played time max, perhapes less... once you get to 14 its a breeze. Once word: Kiting...
